-- Fujian Province to Pursue Legal Action Over Zijin Mine Leak, Xinhua Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-17T02:07:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-17/fujian-province-to-pursue-legal-action-over-zijin-mine-leak-xinhua-says.html

          
          
             Fujian province will pursue legal
action against Zijin Mining Group Co. over pollution by its
copper mine in the region, the Xinhua News Agency reported,
citing a July 16 decision by the local government. The mine will
remain shut pending review by regulators, and Zijing must
protect the interests of the people affected, Xinhua reported.  
